{"tid":1559351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日得萬4人入場撐香港隊 太少太少 集思廣益 11月14日 對巴林要坐爆佢","createTime":"2019-09-10T18:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:25:19.000Z","uid":74632,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3452b5101941416d38d119442ae1f1521656a1","tid":1559351,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"依家呢個時勢 2萬人都冇 係失望 不停叫人吹大雞 都係咁樣 所以要檢討下 我地既宣傳<br />\n<br />\n講返場內 今日氣氛一流 不停叫口號 唱歌 再為香港隊打氣 班球員一定感受到 而且佢地個個都好有拼勁 走上走落 呢場波一定唔係趕客波 個個都有心打場好波比球迷睇<br />\n<br />\n09年 南華4強對科威特SC 坐爆一次 呢場係亞協4強 記得羅生 落晒廣告 黨鐵又有 特別臨開波一星期<br />\n<br />\n足總唔會理 佢地都唔想宣傳 我地應該依家開始不停吹雞入場睇香港隊<br />\n<br />\n最後好想講今日完場走既時候 行落加老連山道 大家都勁團結 勁有士氣 我地一邊叫口號 一邊唱歌 呢個感受完全feel到 我真係好愛香港 <br />\n<br />\n大家要吹定雞 下次要坐爆大球場"},{"pid":"8163beba2378281b95f48932502785e8c1a66509","tid":1559351,"uid":148082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPFk6H6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPFk6H6.jpg&h=2014a435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7002ee6ac7fce10849322ed7e9794398d17076ac","tid":1559351,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"開始應該要 慢慢同朋友講 11月睇波<br />\n<br />\n尋晚萬4人大何唱 叫口號 已經好有威力 <br />\n<br />\n大家要吹雞啦 last兩星期吹大雞 坐爆大球場"},{"pid":"fd72ff7fc22f4339845414a26f3ee8aded45a518","tid":1559351,"uid":19743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"黎緊應該會係10月15對馬來西亞<br />\n但係詳情未公佈<br />\n馬拉同支那有幾FRD <br />\n大家識做"},{"pid":"28df1b3bbc93b5749d2121d4f94651d0f6b2fc9f","tid":1559351,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"希望入場嘅，學埋香港隊打氣beat,幫手撐港隊"},{"pid":"a331a378326217fe7097328afa174738d0406dcd","tid":1559351,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰"},{"pid":"adb3c9a38aa3967a1f4865928debaae7ec412531","tid":1559351,"uid":19549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6c2755ceb53b6a3217215a75369a22dc250dbc7","tid":1559351,"uid":79607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd72ff7fc22f4339845414a26f3ee8aded45a518","tid":1559351,"uid":19743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"黎緊應該會係10月15對馬來西亞<br />\n但係詳情未公佈<br />\n馬拉同支那有幾FRD <br />\n大家識做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"友誼賽？ 友誼賽$80得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d8d7c95b7e140b65c4d753894e469bbd8724d9","tid":1559351,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"[香港隊]我願榮光歸香港正式成為香港國歌嘅唯一方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563420</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6161e7b2cd737faf241f03f9448ef4835141fdd0","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b18272f66e69dead91bf31d316387c6a016cc64c","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"033e912881e5fa8a19279ab19357aeaade0aa86f","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f60c573b4c2d990842b6fdbc041918d9ceaceb22","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0307d95031228c95ce6834a9a1398fc6444df74c","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4767f2930d1290e6afd174e1bb6fb3f2c377bc0","tid":1559351,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n冇咩機會集結 入場啦咁多位"},{"pid":"19e1b76bffbe235b81da1abc19ea5c2d5046382f","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:14:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"18740175a766674a3e56eeec4c7f4af1fe98b773","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"波台黐線佬 Chi Sin Lo<br />\n<br />\n【悼】<br />\n<br />\n波台黐線佬會喺十一月十四日球賽第22分鐘，停止打氣並進行默哀一分鐘，悼念得年22歲嘅周梓樂同學，以及一眾逝去嘅戰友。<br />\n<br />\n理解有球迷當日會穿著黑衫入場作悼念，一直推動「著紅衫撐港隊」文化嘅我哋對此表示尊重。即使今次看台出現兩種顏色，大家支持香港隊同懷念周同學嘅心依然係一致。<br />\n<br />\n我哋亦歡迎球迷繼續身穿紅衫，同時配上黑絲帶或臂纏黑紗，延續港足傳統。<br />\n<br />\n讓我哋將悲痛嘅心情轉化為動力，為香港隊全力打氣，以勝利送別周同學。天祐香港，天祐香港人。<br />\n<br />\n#香港人加油 #香港人反抗 #香港人報仇<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75233405_687298571673817_8184317983644975104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGjRtxvNBEFSpvI6KkibP6XsXRSVGtccmRodcjkGfRMNIRvK3JC3NZP8egoX7PQVt_DTc7bXF7YlwanB_kfr7xFjmk68DH9c6-4nMEEdtOrWA&amp;_nc_oc=AQmtou1-xYO-Kyb9PirKPwHJp6cNiedFIeoys0sRK-N__ccM2t74KgaqDXxlEh8DlWs&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ecf43a3aaa9cb04f8616a4803f3df39e&amp;oe=5E534E39\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F75233405_687298571673817_8184317983644975104_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_eui2%3DAeGjRtxvNBEFSpvI6KkibP6XsXRSVGtccmRodcjkGfRMNIRvK3JC3NZP8egoX7PQVt_DTc7bXF7YlwanB_kfr7xFjmk68DH9c6-4nMEEdtOrWA%26_nc_oc%3DAQmtou1-xYO-Kyb9PirKPwHJp6cNiedFIeoys0sRK-N__ccM2t74KgaqDXxlEh8DlWs%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Decf43a3aaa9cb04f8616a4803f3df39e%26oe%3D5E534E39&h=55adce45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a621f89167e9c6b5e214db0a32168d52ccaa8a20","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ed239337b724da7de886685eb103022274c10a1","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11e3751675ad2d686e94b56d9a7b0f4eb1be0d1d","tid":1559351,"uid":19847,"like":0,"disl